// Standmixer GUI application for the ESP32-S3 Knob Touch LCD 1.8" round display. \
// Implements a 6-mode blender interface with a circular carousel, timer configuration, \
// countdown progress arc and done screen. The state machine transitions through \
// Idle, Setting, Running and Done phases.
// 
// This project also serves as a reference for integrating an external video player \
// (ExternVideo) and external hardware inputs such as the rotary encoder knob via \
// the DeviceClass interface.
// 
// For more information, please visit: https://doc.embedded-wizard.de/
note legend Note5
{
  attr Bounds = <489,240,1080,440>;
}

// State Handling
note group Note7
{
  attr Bounds = <-10,340,230,440>;
}

